## Review Configuration

- **work-item revise severity**: critical
- **work-item revise major count**: 2
- **min lenses**: 3
- **max lenses**: 8

### Lens Catalogue

Use the paths below when constructing agent prompts. Always use the path
from this table rather than constructing paths from the lens name.

| Lens | Path | Source |
|------|------|--------|
| clarity | skills/review/lenses/clarity-lens/SKILL.md | built-in |
| completeness | skills/review/lenses/completeness-lens/SKILL.md | built-in |
| dependency | skills/review/lenses/dependency-lens/SKILL.md | built-in |
| scope | skills/review/lenses/scope-lens/SKILL.md | built-in |
| testability | skills/review/lenses/testability-lens/SKILL.md | built-in |
